  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.6.9">
<l>tārāḷaṉ taṇṇaraṅka vāḷaṉ pūmēl taṉiyāḷaṉ muṉiyāḷa rētta niṉṟa</l>
<l>pērāḷa ṉāyirampē ruṭaiya vāḷaṉ piṉṉaikku maṇavāḷaṉ perumai kēṭpīr</l>
<l>pārāḷa ravarivareṉ ṟaḻuntai yēṟṟa paṭaimaṉṉa ruṭaltuṇiyap parimā vuytta</l>
<l>tērāḷaṉ kōccōḻaṉ cērnta kōyil tirunaṟaiyūr maṇimāṭañ cērmiṉ kaḷē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who would hear of the eminence of Piṉṉai’s groom, him with the garland,</l>
<l rend="indent">him of cool Araṅkam, him whose wife is on a blossom,</l>
<l>Him whose name the sages continue to praise, him with one-thousand names,</l>
<l>Gather at the beautiful raised shrine in Tirunaṟaiyūr, the temple where came</l>
<l rend="indent">the Cōḻa king, the charioteer who drove [his] horses</l>
<l>So that the bodies of kings with armies who opposed [him] in Aḻuntai,</l>
<l rend="indent">being called this and that rulers of the earth, were slashed.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
